title: We Can't Believe Kristin Spent YEARS Never Noticing This About Moe!
description:
Have you arrived at work and completely forgotten how you got there? It's called highway hypnosis, and it almost ruined Bert's morning.
But first, Kristin has a few questions for us. For Bert, it has everything to do with a recent Tiktok trend. And for Moe, it's something we can't believe she didn't notice for four YEARS!
